Class ActionFieldsUnique

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.camerontec.catalys.server.rules.RuleComponentBase

        • com.camerontec.catalys.server.rules.actions.ActionFieldsUnique
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IAction, IRuleComponent, IRulesEngineUniqueFieldsStoreAccessor

    public class ActionFieldsUnique
extends ActionBase
implements IRulesEngineUniqueFieldsStoreAccessor
    Stores a number of fields from the current message to be checked for unique value later by ConditionFieldsUnique.

    If configure tags are empty message will be added/persisted to the store to build the state needed by end of day purge.
